+Builders experience joy through Creation grounded in concreteness and tangible 
+progress. Unlike Creators, whose engagement is driven by open-ended 
+exploration, Builders find satisfaction in making things work: implementing 
+features, wiring components, and producing visible, functional results. Flow 
+arises from steady forward movement, where tools remain predictable and 
+interruptions are minimal. Growth and Resolution support engagement by 
+enabling incremental improvement and problem-solving along the way, but 
+conceptual elegance is secondary to functionality. Builders thrive in 
+environments that allow for incremental construction, stable toolchains, and 
+visible results.
 
