+Stabilizers experience joy primarily through Resolution: ensuring reliability, 
+monitoring system behavior, and preventing regressions. Their engagement is 
+directed toward Contribution to system stability rather than interpersonal 
+support, but the experiential source of joy lies in the resolution process 
+itself. Coherence reinforces their work by providing the structural clarity 
+that makes maintenance meaningful. Novelty is valued only when it reduces 
+future uncertainty. Stabilizers thrive in operational, QA, or 
